28:48.645 --> 28:51.272
-You good?
-I’m good.

28:51.314 --> 28:52.273
That was great.

28:52.315 --> 28:53.191
There you go.

28:56.111 --> 28:57.529
Go on, girl.

28:57.570 --> 29:00.281
Go get changed.

29:08.623 --> 29:09.791
----ing silent treatment.

29:09.833 --> 29:11.292
I feel like in high school.

29:11.334 --> 29:12.585
Just give me
a shout to come down.

29:12.627 --> 29:13.795
It’s going to be a few.

29:13.837 --> 29:15.171
And now I find myself
wondering

29:15.213 --> 29:16.923
