Jess and Lily, how are
the cabins going?

30:03.553 --> 30:04.763
Decent.

30:04.804 --> 30:06.389
We just have to vacuum the
floors

30:06.431 --> 30:08.350
and we’re just having some
technical difficulties with

30:08.391 --> 30:11.686
one of the showers and we just
have to clean one more head.

30:11.728 --> 30:13.355
-Great.
-Very great.

30:13.396 --> 30:16.399
-Can you throw that in there?
-Yeah.

30:16.441 --> 30:17.984
