30:36.378 --> 30:37.629
-Cheffy.
-Yeah.

30:37.671 --> 30:38.922
-Well.
-Thank you.

30:38.963 --> 30:39.923
-Happy.
-Yeah.

30:39.964 --> 30:41.549
I really want to
enjoy this night.

30:41.591 --> 30:43.551
So, that means we need
to really turn it up.

30:43.593 --> 30:44.636
-Chippendales.
-Chippendales.

30:44.678 --> 30:45.970
That’s who we want.

30:46.012 --> 30:47.597
We just need a couple
of the guys inside.

30:47.639 --> 30:48.640
They’re going to strip.

30:48.682 --> 30:49.974
I’m going to organize that.

30:50.016 --> 30:51.851
Thank you so much.

30:51.893 --> 30:53.603
[laughing]

30:58.566 --> 31:00.610
-No, no, no, no.
-Come on, boys.

31:00.652 --> 31:01.986
Luka?

31:03.780 --> 31:05.073
Only get Marcie’s
credit card.

31:15.166 --> 31:19.087
