I’m not going.

38:23.136 --> 38:24.804
Hi!

38:25.847 --> 38:26.681
Thanks.

38:26.723 --> 38:27.932
This whole team is incredible.

38:27.974 --> 38:29.934
We had a beautiful day
with beautiful people.

38:29.976 --> 38:32.437
-Thank you so much.
-Thank you very much.

38:32.479 --> 38:34.189
-It was a pleasure.
-Ciao, Bella.

38:34.230 --> 38:35.398
Ciao.

38:35.440 --> 38:36.608
Well done, everyone.

38:36.649 --> 38:38.735
Out of your whites,
into your reds.

38:38.777 --> 38:43.573
Let’s turn the boat around and
then meet for our tip meeting.

38:43.615 --> 38:45.158
Now we can wear
the red t-shirt, right?

38:45.200 --> 38:46.743
-Yeah.
-Meet on Sundeck.

38:46.785 --> 38:49.204
We’ll just vac dust
the cabins.

38:49.245 --> 38:50.580
White, doing beds.

38:50.622 --> 38:53.416
-Wash and wax.
-Let’s go. You know what I mean?

38:53.458 --> 38:55.001
All crew, all crew.

38:55.043 --> 38:58.338
Let’s meet in the bridge deck
salon for our tip meeting.

38:58.380 --> 39:00.006
The envelope looked
pretty light.

39:00.048 --> 39:02.008
We didn’t do much work
if you think about it.

39:02.050 --> 39:03.009
Speak for yourself.

39:03.051 --> 39:04.344
Thank you, bye.

39:04.386 --> 39:05.887
This guy can’t
----ing help himself, can he?

39:05.929 --> 39:07.639
Something’s going
to go off tonight.

39:07.681 --> 39:10.558
I can just feel it in the air.

39:10.600 --> 39:11.976
We’re more than halfway there.

39:12.018 --> 39:13.687
-How do you do this, Charter?
-It’s fun.

39:13.728 --> 39:17.190
Except for losing
Captain Sunday socks.

39:17.232 --> 39:18.441
You did a great job.

39:18.483 --> 39:20.110
Deck team,
when we docked in Portofino,

39:20.151 --> 39:23.238
one of the most difficult
dockings that we’ve done,

39:23.279 --> 39:24.406
you did an awesome job.

39:24.447 --> 39:25.990
-Thank you.
-You’re on it.

39:26.032 --> 39:26.991
You’re a team.

39:27.033 --> 39:30.662
And this tip is $18,000.

39:30.704 --> 39:34.332
And that is $1252
per person euros.

39:34.374 --> 39:35.458
Thank you, ladies.

39:35.500 --> 39:38.211
Let’s cheers.
Thank you.

39:38.253 --> 39:40.505
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

39:40.547 --> 39:42.507
Don’t spend it all in one place.

39:42.549 --> 39:44.050
I’m going to shower.

39:44.092 --> 39:45.510
We’re going out.

39:45.552 --> 39:47.637
Let’s get this party started.

39:47.679 --> 39:50.015
Got a problem here.
All my clothes is there.

39:50.056 --> 39:51.349
What do you need?

39:51.391 --> 39:54.352
-Do I look like I churn butter?
-No.

39:54.394 --> 39:56.896
[gags]
That’s ----ing strong.

39:56.938 --> 39:57.731
Woo!

39:57.772 --> 39:58.982
Who’s sitting in the back?

39:59.024 --> 40:01.317
Can you put your iPad
back in there, please?

40:01.359 --> 40:02.360
I was just gonna...

40:02.402 --> 40:03.737
Bring the iPad to the club.

40:03.778 --> 40:07.657
I’m putting $100 on Lily
being wasted tonight.

40:07.699 --> 40:10.326
I’m not putting money,
but I will agree on that.

40:10.368 --> 40:12.370
Get out, get out.

40:12.412 --> 40:13.830
[Max vocalizing]

40:15.290 --> 40:16.332
All right.

40:16.374 --> 40:18.543
I’m going to get a margarita.

40:18.585 --> 40:19.961
