40:20.003 --> 40:21.629
Make it three, but with double
tequila for me, please.

40:21.671 --> 40:24.507
-Are you sure?
-Beer? Wine?

40:24.549 --> 40:25.967
Yeah, I’ll have the same.

40:33.933 --> 40:35.268
Bravo.

40:35.310 --> 40:37.520
I think she’s cool.

40:37.562 --> 40:38.563
Has everyone got a drink?

40:38.605 --> 40:39.898
-Cheers.
-Cheers, everyone.

40:39.939 --> 40:41.107
Cheers.

40:48.782 --> 40:51.451
-Mmm.
-It’s good, eh, isn’t it?

40:51.493 --> 40:52.660
Can you do a Liverpool accent?

40:52.702 --> 40:53.787
Can you do
a Liverpool accent?

40:53.828 --> 40:55.580
-No, not Irish.
-No, I can’t.

40:55.622 --> 40:56.831
Nobody can.

40:56.873 --> 40:59.084
-What is that?
-I don’t know. Cheese.

41:18.645 --> 41:21.272
Your banter is above us,
apparently.

41:21.314 --> 41:23.775
So have your banter.

41:23.817 --> 41:25.527
Hey, Lily, is it, is it or not?

41:25.568 --> 41:27.237
They’re playing games. I don’t
know what she’s talking about,

41:27.278 --> 41:28.321
because I see something else.

41:28.363 --> 41:30.365
Wait, what happened?

41:30.407 --> 41:33.451
He wasn’t so brave
without you, but now he is.

41:33.493 --> 41:36.037
Our banter is so sh--.

41:39.165 --> 41:40.291
Oh!

41:40.333 --> 41:41.918
That was a backhander?

41:43.628 --> 41:45.922
Let me go take a wee.

41:49.592 --> 41:51.761
Jack, I know the
game you’re playing.

41:51.803 --> 41:54.347
I feel like Lily’s
already been influenced

41:54.389 --> 41:56.474
by Jack of who I am.

41:56.516 --> 41:57.976
I see it, I hear it,

41:58.018 --> 41:59.978
nothing’s gonna bring
your princess back,

42:00.020 --> 42:02.355
and now you’ve opened
a book of worms.

42:02.397 --> 42:04.190
God damn it.

42:06.860 --> 42:09.237
Later this season on
"Below Deck Med..."

42:09.279 --> 42:10.780
We’re almost there.

42:10.822 --> 42:14.492
We gotta find whatever it is to
keep our attitudes positive.

42:14.534 --> 42:17.662
I’m so ----ing excited.
I am Jacked.

42:17.704 --> 42:20.999
-Woo!
-I thought I was ----ing crazy.

42:21.041 --> 42:22.417
This is chaotic.

42:22.459 --> 42:25.253
They’re out here having
the best time of their life.

42:25.295 --> 42:26.796
Oh!

42:26.838 --> 42:29.716
Where were these guys when I
was getting my teeth extracted?

42:29.758 --> 42:31.551
They would like a
big gay breakfast.

42:31.593 --> 42:33.845
-Oh, stop.
-That’s hilarious.

42:33.887 --> 42:36.639
He’s a problem.
You have to get him...

42:36.681 --> 42:37.682
under control.

42:37.724 --> 42:39.893
Or he’s off the boat.

42:39.934 --> 42:42.687
I think I like Luka
way more than I should.

42:42.729 --> 42:45.065
I like Lily, I really like Lily.

42:47.233 --> 42:48.818
Ow!

42:54.449 --> 42:55.742
Is that your girlfriend
texting you?

42:55.784 --> 42:58.078
Is there something
we don’t know?

42:58.119 --> 42:58.912
No.

42:58.953 --> 43:00.330
We’ve got mutual friends.

43:00.372 --> 43:01.831
Okay.

43:01.873 --> 43:05.126
Look up [bleep] boy and playboy,
and that’s what Luka is.

43:06.461 --> 43:07.420
Lily?

43:07.462 --> 43:08.880
This cannot look like this.

43:10.090 --> 43:12.842
There’s, like, towels
all over the floor.

43:12.884 --> 43:13.927
She is dead weight.

43:13.968 --> 43:16.429
I’ve given her
more than enough.

43:16.471 --> 43:17.972
and she’s just not getting it.

43:18.014 --> 43:21.267
I need you to be more aware.

43:23.019 --> 43:24.187
Where are the deck hands?

43:24.229 --> 43:25.271
I’m here.

43:25.313 --> 43:26.898
Lara’s in the cabin
and Max is down.

43:26.940 --> 43:27.899
We only get you on deck.

43:27.941 --> 43:29.567
That’s not okay.

43:29.609 --> 43:31.027
This is the stuff
that makes me mad.

43:31.069 --> 43:32.237
When she calls and calls,

43:32.278 --> 43:34.072
the deck crew needs
to ----ing answer.

43:34.114 --> 43:35.448
Okay.

43:36.908 --> 43:39.994
My interior team is definitely
hanging on a thread.

43:43.873 --> 43:47.085
I really can’t be handling
men in their 30s.

43:47.127 --> 43:49.921
You’re overstepping boundaries.

43:53.466 --> 43:54.801
Oh, my God.

43:57.178 --> 43:58.930
Sur-----ing-prize!

44:01.182 --> 44:03.935
Jess is definitely trying
to make him jealous.

44:04.811 --> 44:05.895
Sorry, Lil.

44:05.937 --> 44:07.814
He’s a good kisser
I’m just saying.
